"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-2024-olympics-surfing-photo-goes-viral\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  Updated on:  August 2, 2024 / 4:00 PM EDT/ CBS News  A photo of Brazilian Olympic surfer Gabriel Medina, suspended in the air over a wave, went viral earlier this week.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999948967386604, \"rank\": 5.012813510474418e-06, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His index finger is pointed to the sky as he's captured celebrating his recording-breaking 9.90 single-wave score in the fifth heat of the third round of men's surfing on Monday.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The2024 Paris Olympicssurfing competition is taking place on the French Polynesianisland of Tahiti.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999988799573, \"rank\": 1.120074532666024e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stunning photo had many people questioning whether it was too good to be true, and speculating whether it was made by artificial intelligence or Photoshopped.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Photograph_manipulation\", \"score\": 0.9999708759006073, \"rank\": 2.912494767754184e-05, \"text\": \"Photoshopped\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Photograph_manipulation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Photograph_manipulation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Jerome Brouillet, the Agence France-Presse photographer who took the shot, explained that gettingthe picturewas a mix of luck, expertise and preparation.\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"score\": 0.9999973112585161, \"rank\": 2.6881730141272854e-06, \"text\": \"Jerome\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}, {\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love this shot, for sure, because it's special, and I think I will get only one shot like that in my entire life,\\\" Brouillet said.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told CBS News he had an idea of what Medina would do after a successful ride.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999948967386604, \"rank\": 5.012813510474418e-06, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8450271218740597e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Gabriel used to make this kind of gesture at the end of his surfing, when he catches a good wave,\\\" Brouillet said.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, I was aiming somewhere on the wave, because you can miss the jump,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And, when I saw him, I pressed the button and I shot about six, seven shots.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was shooting 10 shots a second.\\\"\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by CBS News (@cbsnews)  \\\"I looked at the shots, and I selected two photos,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999948967386604, \"rank\": 5.012813510474418e-06, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The second one was this shot because of the alignment of this gesture was special.\\\"\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The picture went viral as soon as it was published and Brouillet's phone was flooded with notifications.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media was abuzz with comments, including many that debunked the AI claims.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People were saying, \\\"'Look at the video here.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see the line-up of the board on the video and the other side,'\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brouillet said he was surprised by how much attention this photo got since it is a celebratory photo, not a classic surfing shot.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he now realizes that the picture speaks to everyone and highlights the sport.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If everyone is talking about surfing by a celebration shot, it's perfect, and the surfing world is winning.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all winning.\\\"\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(04:32)  Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": []}]}"